        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
            
  <section class="help rail rail-reversed">
    <h1>
      Poisoned? Get Expert Help.
    </h1>
    <p>Don't guess what you should do. Get accurate Poison Control answers online or by phone. Both are free and confidential.</p><a href='http://triage.webpoisoncontrol.org/#/reset' class='button button-alt' target='_blank' >Get HELP ONLINE</a>
    <p>
      <span>or</span>
      CALL
      <span class="number">1-800-222-1222</span>
    </p>
  </section>


  <section class="rail rail-icon">

    <h1>
